│ \n    // Don't sink instructions that produce no values.\n   │
│ if (I->getType()->isVoidTy())\n      continue;\n             │
│ ```\n\n### 5. Conclusion\n\nThe `gvn-sink` pass was failing  │
│ because it incorrectly tried to sink `void`-returning `asm`  │
│ calls, which do not produce values and cannot be operands in │
